rit when you pass through this body through this lifetime.', 19401, 0), (94682, 'That''s the weirdest thing about being cut off from life. Everything gets washed out or muted or recedes into the background except for other people''s laughter. Other people''s laughter gets very loud and jarring. It penetrates. It is a reminder that other people live.', 19402, 0), (94683, 'Enlightenment is making friendship with the whole existence.', 379, 0), (94684, 'There are twenty one mystical dimensions of consciousness. Enlightenment is abiding in the highest three dimensions of consciousness.', 379, 0), (94685, 'The observer of the soul cannot penetrate into the soul, but there doubtless is a margin where he comes into contact with it.', 629, 0), (94686, 'Immersed in surrender and gratitude, celestial pearls of wisdom form rosaries of prayer that entangle with my soul.', 19403, 0), (94687, 'A strong soul recovers from any suffering.', 2878, 0), (94688, 'Sufferings lead a man to his soul.', 2878, 0), (94689, 'Keep seeking the spirituality of thy soul.', 2878, 0), (94690, 'In suffering, I got to know my soul.', 2878, 0), (94691, 'Your soul is always trying to guide you in your true life direction towards your highest good and greatest happiness.', 19401, 0), (94692, 'Trust your soul.It alone knows what you are here to do in this lifetime and what will actually make you happy.', 19401, 0), (94693, 'In deep suffering, I got to know divinity within my soul.', 2878, 0), (94694, 'Nature''s voice and Nature''s beauty---God''s soothing and purifying angels of the soul---speak to me most tenderly and most happily, at such times as these.', 3317, 0), (94695, 'Music is the soul food.', 2878, 0), (94696, 'It is sad, people what to control others. But they have not learned to know their soul.', 2878, 0), (94697, 'Seek to know your sacred soul.', 2878, 0), (94698, 'Do not forget to care for your body, soul and spirit.', 2878, 0), (94699, 'The strength of the spirit sustains the soul.', 2878,