he new class people with their cars and their money and their tellies and their stupid vulgarities and their stupid crawling imitations of the bourgeoisie.(...)The New People are still the poor people, it is the new form of poverty. The others hadn''t any money and these haven''t any soul.', 1452, 0), (95291, 'To breathe,to breathe is nothing more than confirmation of the existence of your soulwhether you believe it or not,whether you live or cease to fight', 19463, 0), (95292, 'Love with all your heart, soul and mind.', 2878, 0), (95293, 'Humanity is completely consumed with the pleasures of the flesh', 19464, 0), (95294, 'Love is like sunshine', 19465, 0), (95295, 'Your soul was bought for a price far greater than the world on the cross', 19466, 0), (95296, 'Life is a song made of the musical rhythm of the body, words of the mind and the melodious silence of the soul.', 6319, 0), (95297, 'Love rekindles the soul of every man.', 2878, 0), (95298, 'I am a soul, and I have a body. We don''t learn about people by studying their bodies. We learn about people by finding out how they feel, what they think, what they''re passionate about, what their worldview is, and so forth....So my conclusion is that there''s more to me than my conscious life and my body. In fact, I am a ''self,'' or an ''I,'' that cannot be seen or touched unless I manifest myself through my behavior or my talk. I have free will because I am a ''self,'' or a soul, and I''m not just a brain. ~J.P. Moreland, PHD~', 9195, 0), (95299, 'Divinities of the soul are life, light and love.', 2878, 0), (95300, 'When I connect with the animals around me, I connect with their soul. I believe where there is a soul, there is a journey and a purpose.', 19467, 0);
INSERT INTO quotes (id, content, author_id, views) VALUES (95301, 'Disappointments are to the soul what a thunderstorm is to the air.', 1988, 0), (95302, 'Sometimes the heart speaks, and the brain does not understand the language.', 19468, 0), (95303, 'If God is really my Father, I have rights, and He has responsibilities. I hereby claim my birthright to be protected, educated, and provided for!', 5164, 0), (95304, 'Negative thought saps a person’s strength.Positive thought is healthy to the soul.', 2878, 0), (95305, 'Death has only one hand glove... so it takes away the body, but leaves behind the impacts. Difference makers live twice; in body and in impacts... The former is temporal but the later lasts long!', 3301, 0), (95306, 'Beauty of music enlightens the soul and fills it with ecstasy.', 2586, 0), (95307, 'The machinery of propaganda may pack their minds with falsehood and deny them truth for many generations of time. But the soul of man thus held in trance, or frozen in a long night, can be awakened by a spark coming from God knows where, and in a moment the whole structure of lies and oppression is on trial for its life.', 1150, 0), (95308, 'My soul is exceedingly joyful.', 2878, 0), (95309, 'The deepest-lying and most pervasive part of character is disposition: it accompanies us everywhere, and shows itself in all we do. It is the attitude of the soul toward life, the way in which we accept our situation and our daily experiences. On the inner side it gives color and tone to our own conscious life: on the outer side it pervades and modifies our conduct toward others and our reactions to events. A good disposition is indispensable to good character, though of course not all of character; without it one cannot hope for perfection; even with it one may fail through lack of higher elements. It is a sort of foundation layer.', 19469, 0), (95310, 'Negative thoughts crashed the spirit, weaken the soul and make the body sick.', 2878, 0), (95311, 'Hope is what keeps the soul alive.', 2878, 0), (95312, 'Happiness is ''happening'' in the good souls, those God loves. That love is mirrored in terms of Happiness.', 19470, 0), (95313, 'Awake my great soul.Awake my great spirit.Awake my great strength.', 2878, 0), (95314, 'Reach out to your great spirit and soul.', 2878, 0), (95315, 'Don''t come to God because you have a problem', 19471, 0), (95316, 'What the fertilizer does to the germinating plant is what happiness does for a depressed soul... What anger does to a person is what an acid does to its container!', 3301, 0), (95317, 'Sometimes it is better to say ‘no’ and lose your job than it is to say ‘yes’ and lose your soul.', 4406, 0), (95318, 'Mankind''s glorious and people''s happy ending is inevitable. No one will be left behind.', 5164, 0), (95319, 'Spirituality is conversation with God, everything else is just religious custom.', 5164, 0), (95320, 'Positive thought is healthy to the soul.', 2878, 0), (95321, 'Adversity tests what the soul can endure.', 2878, 0), (95322, 'In fact take my body who will, take it I say, it is not me. And therefore three cheers for Nantucket; and come a stove boat and stove body when they will, for stave my soul, Jove himself cannot.', 19472, 0), (95323, 'May the Creator ignite the spark of light within our soul.', 2878, 0), (95324, 'My real soul...? It’s real only when it’s independent...', 631, 0), (95325, 'The spirit awaken, the soul revive.', 2878, 0), (95326, 'Music empowers the soul with great strength.', 2878, 0), (95327, 'Awake my great soul.', 2878, 0), (95328, 'they say every living thing requires proper nutrition to survive, they also say music is food for the soul, if that was true i would hav been long dead, hence proved that the soul which survive on music is not a soul but a desire and desires don''t die until killed, we should be concerned about the soul which will be held accountable after our deaths, we should make sure our soul is not on dieting now a days', 19473, 0), (95329, 