urse, humor is always a plus. (158)', 19566, 0), (95981, 'Leadership is fundamentally about credibility.', 19567, 0), (95982, 'We thrive when we are pulled by the future, not pushed by the past.', 18535, 0), (95983, 'Despite the continual rise of the knowledge worker over the last 60 years, we haven’t done enough to question “how we’ve always done things” and redefine effectiveness in organizations.', 18535, 0), (95984, 'More than a phone call or likes on facebook - Leadership', 5782, 0), (95985, 'The place where "me & I" does not exist - Leadership', 5782, 0), (95986, 'Leadership, a daily development.', 5782, 0), (95987, 'I am not afraid of how the LGTB community reacts on Christians, but how Christians react back.', 5782, 0), (95988, 'Leadership: In love with the team, not the spotlights.', 5782, 0), (95989, 'Leadership, where happiness and work works.', 5782, 0), (95990, 'Having and understanding of the ''why'' will help having an understanding of the ''how''.', 8566, 0), (95991, 'To lead solely on the behalf of those being led is the utter pinnacle of fatherhood, and it is sad that so few ever stand on the summit.', 4397, 0), (95992, 'One of the first things you learn as a leader, whether you choose the position of have it forced upon you, is that leadership is as much about what you don''t say as what you do say.', 501, 0), (95993, 'Before you follow somebody, ask whom is he following.', 5782, 0), (95994, 'Leadership gives more than it can receive.', 5782, 0), (95995, '90% of our Leadership happens when we do not speak.', 5782, 0), (95996, 'You can''t be richer than your trust in your partners.', 5782, 0), (95997, 'Look forward to be a learner. The leader comes along.', 5782, 0), (95998, 'Too many train their speaking than their listening.', 5782, 0), (95999, 'You can''t build bigger businesses than your level of leadership.', 5782, 0), (96000, 'Leaders lead by serving.', 5782, 0);
